Velour Students in conjunction with Charles University Choers
The Festival Festa Academica offers for the third time celebrations that connect the International Student Day with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical part.
During the festival there are 20 choers of higher schools and secondary classes.
The festival nail is made up of two concerts organized on November 17.
"Charles University has an important part in this festival."
